The paper proposes a deep learning approach for extracting drug-drug interactions from biomedical text. This involves natural language processing and classification, which are common topics in the computer science sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
